1
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:10,511
EARTH-STYLE
DISTRESS SIGNAL--SOS.

2
00:00:10,636 --> 00:00:12,596
I'VE ANSWERED IT
ON ALL FREQUENCIES, SIR.

3
00:00:12,721 --> 00:00:13,347
THEY DON'T REPLY.

4
00:00:13,472 --> 00:00:15,891
NOT A VESSEL,
A GROUND SOURCE.

5
00:00:16,016 --> 00:00:17,852
THE THIRD PLANET
IN THIS SOLAR SYSTEM,

6
00:00:17,977 --> 00:00:19,728
ACCORDING
TO MY INSTRUMENTS.

7
00:00:21,981 --> 00:00:22,481
DIRECTLY AHEAD.

8
00:00:22,606 --> 00:00:24,900
DEFINITELY AN
EARTH-STYLE SIGNAL.

9
00:00:25,024 --> 00:00:28,445
WE'RE HUNDREDS
OF LIGHT YEARS
FROM EARTH, MR. SPOCK.

10
00:00:28,570 --> 00:00:31,699
NO COLONIES OR VESSELS
OUT THIS FAR.

11
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:39,832
MEASURING THE PLANET NOW,
CAPTAIN.

12
00:00:39,957 --> 00:00:41,500
IT'S SPHEROID-SHAPED.

13
00:00:41,625 --> 00:00:46,171
CIRCUMFERENCE--
24,874 MILES.

14
00:00:46,296 --> 00:00:50,091
MASS--6 TIMES 10
TO THE 21st POWER TONS.

15
00:00:50,217 --> 00:00:54,054
MEAN DENSITY--5.517.

16
00:00:54,179 --> 00:00:56,056
ATMOSPHERE...

17
00:00:56,181 --> 00:00:58,517
OXYGEN, NITROGEN.

18
00:00:58,642 --> 00:01:00,352
EARTH!

19
00:01:01,562 --> 00:01:05,065
NOT<i> THE</i> EARTH,
ANOTHER EARTH.

20
00:01:05,190 --> 00:01:07,359
ANOTHER EARTH?

21
00:01:18,579 --> 00:01:22,624
SPACE--
THE FINAL FRONTIER.

22
00:01:22,750 --> 00:01:26,336
THESE ARE THE VOYAGES
OF THE STARSHIP<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

23
00:01:26,461 --> 00:01:27,379
ITS FIVE-YEAR MISSION--

24
00:01:27,504 --> 00:01:31,466
TO EXPLORE
STRANGE NEW WORLDS...

25
00:01:31,592 --> 00:01:34,803
TO SEEK OUT NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS...

26
00:01:35,888 --> 00:01:39,098
TO BOLDLY GO WHERE
NO MAN HAS GONE BEFORE.

27
00:02:11,506 --> 00:02:15,010
CAPTAIN'S LOG,
STARDATE 2713.5.

28
00:02:15,135 --> 00:02:17,262
IN THE DISTANT REACHES
OF OUR GALAXY,

29
00:02:17,387 --> 00:02:19,264
WE HAVE MADE
AN ASTONISHING DISCOVERY--

30
00:02:19,389 --> 00:02:21,892
EARTH-TYPE RADIO SIGNALS
COMING FROM A PLANET

31
00:02:22,017 --> 00:02:24,311
WHICH APPARENTLY
IS AN EXACT DUPLICATE

32
00:02:24,436 --> 00:02:25,145
OF THE EARTH.

33
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:26,647
IT SEEMS IMPOSSIBLE...

34
00:02:26,772 --> 00:02:28,899
BUT THERE IT IS.

35
00:02:29,024 --> 00:02:30,692
HOLD US IN A FIXED
ORBIT, MR. SPOCK.

36
00:02:30,818 --> 00:02:31,902
AFFIRMATIVE, CAPTAIN.

37
00:02:32,027 --> 00:02:33,320
STILL NO RESPONSE,
COMMUNICATIONS?

38
00:02:33,445 --> 00:02:34,905
NONE, CAPTAIN.

39
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:36,073
WE'LL BEAM DOWN.

40
00:02:36,197 --> 00:02:37,866
ALERT SECURITY.

41
00:02:37,992 --> 00:02:40,995
PREPARE TO TRANSPORT
LANDING PARTY
TO SURFACE.

42
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:43,122
WE'LL LAND
IN THE VICINITY

43
00:02:43,246 --> 00:02:45,624
OF THE DISTRESS SIGNALS
NOW BEING RECEIVED.

44
00:03:16,571 --> 00:03:18,573
IDENTICAL.

45
00:03:18,699 --> 00:03:22,036
EARTH...AS IT WAS
IN THE EARLY 1900s.

46
00:03:22,161 --> 00:03:25,039
MORE THE,
UH, MID-1900s.

47
00:03:25,164 --> 00:03:27,624
I WOULD SAY, CAPTAIN,
APPROXIMATELY 1960.

48
00:03:27,749 --> 00:03:29,668
BUT WHERE IS
EVERYBODY?

49
00:03:29,793 --> 00:03:32,253
READINGS INDICATE THAT
NATURAL DETERIORATION

50
00:03:32,379 --> 00:03:33,338
HAS BEEN TAKING PLACE
ON THIS PLANET

51
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:35,132
FOR AT LEAST
SEVERAL CENTURIES.

52
00:03:35,256 --> 00:03:37,092
YOU MEAN THERE'S
NO ONE ALIVE?

53
00:03:37,217 --> 00:03:38,844
NOT CONCLUSIVE, YEOMAN.

54
00:03:38,969 --> 00:03:40,679
THE EVIDENCE
WOULD SUGGEST

55
00:03:40,804 --> 00:03:43,724
THAT THE DISTRESS SIGNAL
IS AUTOMATED.

56
00:03:46,309 --> 00:03:48,854
NOW, THIS IS MARVELOUS--

57
00:03:48,979 --> 00:03:50,814
THE MOST HORRIBLE
CONGLOMERATION

58
00:03:50,939 --> 00:03:53,650
OF ANTIQUE ARCHITECTURE
I'VE EVER SEEN.

59
00:04:06,788 --> 00:04:08,916
MR. SPOCK.

60
00:04:12,627 --> 00:04:14,713
[TRICYCLE BELL RINGS]

61
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:32,856
[WHEEL SQUEAKS]

62
00:04:32,981 --> 00:04:35,442
MINE!

63
00:04:35,567 --> 00:04:36,568
MINE!

64
00:04:38,112 --> 00:04:39,613
MINE!

65
00:04:40,822 --> 00:04:41,907
MINE!

66
