MINE!

67
00:04:47,370 --> 00:04:47,955
MINE!

68
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:50,498
MINE! MINE!

69
00:05:11,103 --> 00:05:13,147
[SOBBING]
IT'S BROKE.

70
00:05:13,272 --> 00:05:18,568
SOMEBODY...BROKE IT.

71
00:05:19,987 --> 00:05:21,571
FIX.

72
00:05:22,781 --> 00:05:24,866
SOMEBODY...PLEASE FIX.

73
00:05:24,992 --> 00:05:26,660
[SOBBING]

74
00:05:26,785 --> 00:05:28,829
OF COURSE SOMEBODY
WILL FIX IT.

75
00:05:28,954 --> 00:05:31,331
DEFINITELY HUMANOID,
IN SPITE OF
THE DISTORTION.

76
00:05:31,456 --> 00:05:33,583
BUT WITH THE MIND
OF A CHILD.

77
00:05:34,751 --> 00:05:36,586
[GASPING]

78
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:41,258
BONES,
WHAT IS IT?

79
00:05:41,382 --> 00:05:43,927
A SEIZURE
OF SOME TYPE.

80
00:05:50,184 --> 00:05:51,685
WE WANT
TO HELP YOU.

81
00:05:51,810 --> 00:05:53,561
LIAR!

82
00:05:54,938 --> 00:05:57,524
NEVER...NEVER!

83
00:05:57,649 --> 00:05:59,526
NEVER! NEVER!

84
00:05:59,651 --> 00:06:00,610
NEVER! NEVER!

85
00:06:00,735 --> 00:06:02,361
[LAUGHING]

86
00:06:02,487 --> 00:06:03,822
NEVER!

87
00:06:16,501 --> 00:06:18,045
IT'S DEAD.

88
00:06:19,129 --> 00:06:20,881
IT'S INCREDIBLE.

89
00:06:21,006 --> 00:06:22,841
WHAT?

90
00:06:22,966 --> 00:06:24,383
ITS METABOLIC RATE--

91
00:06:24,509 --> 00:06:25,384
IT'S IMPOSSIBLY HIGH,

92
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:28,429
AS IF IT'S
BURNING ITSELF UP,

93
00:06:28,555 --> 00:06:30,932
ALMOST AS IF
IT AGED A CENTURY

94
00:06:31,058 --> 00:06:33,434
IN JUST THE PAST
FEW MINUTES.

95
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,645
[FOOTSTEPS]

96
00:06:36,897 --> 00:06:38,648
COME ON!

97
00:06:54,789 --> 00:06:56,583
[CREAKING]

98
00:07:20,607 --> 00:07:22,067
HOW OLD IS THIS THING?

99
00:07:22,192 --> 00:07:22,901
ABOUT 300 YEARS.

100
00:07:23,026 --> 00:07:25,695
[THUMPING]

101
00:07:32,035 --> 00:07:33,453
[GROAN]

102
00:07:33,578 --> 00:07:34,871
COME OUT!

103
00:07:34,996 --> 00:07:38,083
WE MEAN YOU NO HARM.

104
00:07:46,716 --> 00:07:48,260
DON'T HURT ME, PLEASE.

105
00:07:48,385 --> 00:07:50,553
I'M NOT
GOING TO HURT YOU.

106
00:07:50,678 --> 00:07:53,848
NO, PLEASE, DON'T.
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

107
00:07:53,974 --> 00:07:55,225
I WON'T HURT YOU.

108
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,310
NO, PLEASE, DON'T.

109
00:07:56,435 --> 00:07:57,227
I ONLY WANT TO TALK.

110
00:07:57,352 --> 00:07:58,603
NO, DON'T. DON'T HURT.

111
00:07:58,728 --> 00:07:59,479
COME ON.

112
00:07:59,604 --> 00:08:00,688
DON'T, PLEASE.

113
00:08:00,814 --> 00:08:02,607
I WON'T HURT YOU.
DON'T HURT ME.

114
00:08:02,732 --> 00:08:04,234
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

115
00:08:04,359 --> 00:08:05,068
COME ON.

116
00:08:05,193 --> 00:08:06,527
WE WON'T HURT YOU,
SWEETHEART.

117
00:08:06,653 --> 00:08:07,862
WE'RE YOUR FRIENDS.

118
00:08:07,988 --> 00:08:10,824
NO, SHH!

119
00:08:10,949 --> 00:08:13,076
TAKE THE GUARDS.
HAVE A LOOK OUTSIDE.

120
00:08:13,201 --> 00:08:14,535
RADIOACTIVE READINGS,
CHEMICAL POLLUTION,

121
00:08:14,661 --> 00:08:15,912
ANY FURTHER SIGN OF LIFE.

122
00:08:16,037 --> 00:08:17,122
RIGHT, CAPTAIN.

123
00:08:20,667 --> 00:08:22,543
I WONDER WHAT
HAPPENED TO HER

124
00:08:22,669 --> 00:08:26,298
THAT SHE SHOULD
BE SO TERRIFIED OF US.

125
00:08:36,224 --> 00:08:38,935
[TRICORDER WHINES]

126
00:09:03,584 --> 00:09:06,463
BUT I REMEMBER THE THINGS
YOU GRUPS DID--

127
00:09:06,587 --> 00:09:09,966
BURNING, YELLING,
HURTING PEOPLE.

128
00:09:10,091 --> 00:09:13,345
WE DIDN'T
DO ANYTHING
LIKE THAT.

129
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:15,430
YOU'RE NOT
GOING TO HURT?

130
00:09:15,555 --> 00:09:17,140
WELL,
OF COURSE NOT.

131
00:09:17,265 --> 00:09:20,477
WE'RE HERE
TO HELP.

132
00:09:20,601 --> 00:09:22,479
GRUPS DON'T HELP.

133
00:09:22,603 --> 00:09:25,524
BUT WE WILL.

134
00:09:25,648 --> 00:09:26,900
WHAT HAPPENED
HERE?

135
00:09:27,025 --> 00:09:29,110
WHERE IS
EVERYBODY?

136
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:32,655
YOU KNOW.

137
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:34,241
NO, I DON'T.

138
00:09:34,366 --> 00:09:36,951
WON'T
YOU TELL ME?

139
00:09:37,077 --> 00:09:38,453
YOU GOT A FOOLIE,
IS THAT IT?

140
00:09:38,578 --> 00:09:41,415
YOU WANT ME
TO PLAY, BUT I CAN'T.

141
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:43,375
I DON'T KNOW THE RULES.
I'VE GOT TO KNOW THE RULES.

142
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:44,084
FOOLIE?

143
00:09:44,209 --> 00:09:46,711
A GAME, YOU KNOW.

144
00:09:46,836 --> 00:09:48,963
I CAN'T PLAY A GAME
WITHOUT RULES.

145
00:09:49,089 --> 00:09:52,926
EVEN GRUPS
OUGHT TO KNOW THAT.

146
00:09:53,051 --> 00:09:54,302
WHAT ARE GRUPS?

147
00:09:54,428 --> 00:09:56,137
YOU ARE.

148
00:09:57,764 --> 00:10:01,059
THEY WILL,
WHEN ONLIES GET OLD.

149
00:10:01,184 --> 00:10:03,019
GROWNUPS.

150
00:10:07,482 --> 00:10:11,611
YOU SAID SOMETHING
ABOUT THE...GRUPS
DOING BAD THINGS--

151
00:10:11,736 --> 00:10:13,447
YELLING, HURTING,
BURNING.

152
00:10:13,572 --> 00:10:15,449
THAT WAS WHEN THEY
STARTED TO GET SICK

153
00:10:15,574 --> 00:10:17,075
IN THE BEFORE TIME.

154
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:20,912
WE HID,
THEN THEY WERE GONE.

155
00:10:21,037 --> 00:10:22,247
AM I DOING ALL RIGHT?

156
00:10:22,372 --> 00:10:24,624
YOU'RE DOING FINE.

157
00:10:25,584 --> 00:10:27,586
YOU SAID THE GRUPS
GOT SICK.

158
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:30,630
IS THAT WHY
THERE AREN'T ANY
OF THEM AROUND?

159
00:10:30,755 --> 00:10:33,383
YES. THEY DIED,

160
00:10:35,009 --> 00:10:36,636
BUT THAT WAS AFTER
THE AWFUL THINGS.

161
00:10:37,804 --> 00:10:39,389
A PLAGUE, CAPTAIN.

162
00:10:39,514 --> 00:10:42,100
THAT COULD EXPLAIN
A LOT OF IT.

163
00:10:44,185 --> 00:10:48,148
BUT WHAT
ABOUT THE CHILDREN,
THE...ONLIES?

164
00:10:48,273 --> 00:10:49,483
DIDN'T THE AWFUL
THINGS AFFECT THEM?

165
00:10:49,608 --> 00:10:51,901
OF COURSE NOT.
WE'RE HERE, AREN'T WE?

166
00:10:52,026 --> 00:10:54,279
MORE OF YOU?
HOW MANY?

167
00:10:54,404 --> 00:10:56,573
ALL THERE ARE.

168
00:11:14,257 --> 00:11:16,259
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

169
00:11:16,384 --> 00:11:18,303
MIRI.

170
00:11:18,428 --> 00:11:20,847
MIRI...

171
00:11:20,972 --> 00:11:22,681
PRETTY NAME...

172
00:11:24,518 --> 00:11:25,935
FOR A PRETTY
YOUNG WOMAN.

173
00:11:30,731 --> 00:11:32,984
PRETTY?

174
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:36,530
VERY PRETTY.

175
00:12:08,811 --> 00:12:10,271
[BANG]

176
00:12:10,397 --> 00:12:12,273
GUARDS!

177
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:25,579
COVER ME.

178
00:12:34,504 --> 00:12:36,715
[CHILDREN]
♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

179
00:12:57,527 --> 00:12:59,362
