♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

183
00:13:06,035 --> 00:13:07,912
♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

184
00:13:08,037 --> 00:13:09,205
♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

185
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:10,290
♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

186
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:12,292
♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

187
00:13:12,417 --> 00:13:14,168
♪ NYAH YAH YAH-YAH YAH ♪

188
00:13:19,299 --> 00:13:21,842
CHILDREN, CAPTAIN,
LOTS OF THEM.

189
00:13:21,968 --> 00:13:23,720
WE COULDN'T BEGIN
TO GET CLOSE TO THEM.

190
00:13:23,844 --> 00:13:26,139
THEY JUST SEEMED
TO SCURRY AWAY...

191
00:13:26,264 --> 00:13:27,599
LIKE ANIMALS.

192
00:13:27,724 --> 00:13:28,308
ONLY CHILDREN.

193
00:13:28,433 --> 00:13:30,893
MIRI SAID
ALL THE ADULTS DIED.

194
00:13:31,018 --> 00:13:34,272
THAT CREATURE
WHICH ATTACKED US
WAS CERTAINLY NO CHILD.

195
00:13:34,397 --> 00:13:37,024
PERHAPS IT DIED
OF THE DISEASE

196
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:39,152
THE GIRL'S
TALKING ABOUT.

197
00:13:39,277 --> 00:13:41,154
THERE MUST BE
RECORDS SOMEWHERE...

198
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:44,991
AND ANSWERS TO SOME
OF OUR QUESTIONS.

199
00:13:46,033 --> 00:13:47,702
MIRI...

200
00:13:48,286 --> 00:13:50,664
DO YOU
KNOW ANY BUILDINGS

201
00:13:50,789 --> 00:13:52,707
WHERE THE DOCTORS
USED TO WORK?

202
00:13:52,831 --> 00:13:54,334
YES, I KNOW THAT.

203
00:13:54,459 --> 00:13:56,419
THEM AND THEIR PILLS
AND THINGS.

204
00:13:56,544 --> 00:13:57,086
WILL YOU
TAKE ME THERE?

205
00:13:57,211 --> 00:13:58,879
THAT'S A BAD PLACE.

206
00:13:59,005 --> 00:14:00,590
IT'S IMPORTANT.

207
00:14:02,592 --> 00:14:03,551
PLEASE?

208
00:14:03,677 --> 00:14:05,928
ALL RIGHT.

209
00:14:09,641 --> 00:14:11,685
DO YOU HAVE A NAME, TOO?

210
00:14:11,810 --> 00:14:13,144
YES.

211
00:14:13,269 --> 00:14:14,270
IT'S JIM.

212
00:14:14,395 --> 00:14:16,189
I LIKE THAT NAME.

213
00:14:16,314 --> 00:14:17,774
GOOD.

214
00:14:17,898 --> 00:14:20,151
I LIKE YOURS, TOO.

215
00:14:20,276 --> 00:14:22,236
I LIKE YOU.

216
00:14:23,321 --> 00:14:24,698
DO YOU REALLY?

217
00:14:24,823 --> 00:14:28,242
I WOULDN'T LIE
TO YOU.

218
00:14:29,243 --> 00:14:31,329
I WOULDN'T LIE
TO YOU EITHER, JIM.

219
00:14:33,206 --> 00:14:35,583
I REMEMBER THE GRUPS,
BUT YOU'RE NICE.

220
00:14:35,709 --> 00:14:37,711
YOU'RE DIFFERENT.

221
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:41,589
WHY, THANK YOU.

222
00:14:47,554 --> 00:14:48,971
IT'S ALREADY STARTING.

223
00:14:49,096 --> 00:14:50,724
I KNEW IT WOULD.

224
00:14:50,849 --> 00:14:53,476
JUST LIKE IT DID
WITH THE GRUPS.

225
00:14:53,601 --> 00:14:55,854
IT'LL SPREAD ALL OVER YOU,
AND YOU'LL YELL.

226
00:14:55,978 --> 00:14:58,439
YOU'LL TRY
TO HURT EVERYBODY.
THEN YOU'LL DIE.

227
00:14:58,565 --> 00:15:01,526
I KNEW IT WOULD!
I KNEW IT WOULD!

228
00:15:13,872 --> 00:15:17,917
CAPTAIN'S LOG,
STARDATE 2713.6.

229
00:15:18,042 --> 00:15:20,336
THE BUILDING
MIRI LED US TO

230
00:15:20,461 --> 00:15:23,130
ALSO HOUSED AN AUTOMATIC
TRANSMISSION STATION,

231
00:15:23,256 --> 00:15:24,549
WHICH SENT OUT
THE SIGNALS

232
00:15:24,674 --> 00:15:25,925
THAT DREW US
TO THIS PLANET.

233
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:28,177
WE ALSO DISCOVERED
SOMETHING ELSE--

234
00:15:28,302 --> 00:15:29,763
THAT THE BLUE SPLOTCHES

235
00:15:29,888 --> 00:15:31,222
CHARACTERISTIC
OF THE UNKNOWN DISEASE

236
00:15:31,347 --> 00:15:34,141
HAD APPEARED
ON EACH OF US,

237
00:15:34,267 --> 00:15:36,977
WITH THE EXCEPTION
OF MR. SPOCK.

238
00:15:37,103 --> 00:15:39,731
THERE WAS A WELL-EQUIPPED
LABORATORY IN THE BUILDING.

239
00:15:39,856 --> 00:15:41,733
DR. McCOY TOOK TISSUE SAMPLES
OF EACH OF US

240
00:15:41,858 --> 00:15:44,903
IN AN ATTEMPT TO ISOLATE
THE ORGANISM RESPONSIBLE.

241
00:15:45,027 --> 00:15:48,782
A VERITABLE
ZOO OF BACTERIA.

242
00:15:50,366 --> 00:15:52,744
BEAM DOWN
A BIOCOMPUTER

243
00:15:52,869 --> 00:15:54,662
AND A PORTABLE
ELECTRONIC MICROSCOPE.

244
00:15:54,788 --> 00:15:55,872
IF I'M GOING TO BE
DEALING WITH VIRUSES,

245
00:15:55,996 --> 00:15:58,249
I'M GOING TO NEED
BETTER EQUIPMENT
THAN I HAVE HERE.

246
00:15:58,374 --> 00:16:01,085
YES, DOCTOR.
CAPTAIN KIRK.

247
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:02,128
YES, LIEUTENANT?

248
00:16:02,253 --> 00:16:03,170
I'VE GOT VOLUNTEERS
STANDING BY

249
00:16:03,296 --> 00:16:04,171
READY TO HELP YOU, SIR.

250
00:16:04,297 --> 00:16:06,674
UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES

251
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,050
DO I WANT ANYONE
TO BEAM DOWN FROM THE SHIP.

252
00:16:08,175 --> 00:16:10,136
WE CAN'T TAKE
ANY CHANCES WITH
FURTHER CONTAMINATION.

253
00:16:10,261 --> 00:16:12,764
BUT, CAPTAIN,
IF YOU BECOME TOO ILL--

254
00:16:12,889 --> 00:16:13,807
MY ORDERS STILL STAND,
LIEUTENANT.

255
00:16:13,932 --> 00:16:15,934
YOU CAN HELP US BEST BY
CLEARING THE COMPUTER BANKS

256
00:16:16,058 --> 00:16:17,977
AND STANDING BY.
KIRK OUT.

257
00:16:20,897 --> 00:16:22,315
BONES.

258
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,733
HMM?

259
00:16:23,858 --> 00:16:25,192
WHY DO YOU THINK

260
00:16:25,318 --> 00:16:28,154
THE SYMPTOMS
HAVEN'T APPEARED
IN MR. SPOCK?

261
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:31,449
I DON'T KNOW.

262
00:16:31,574 --> 00:16:33,952
PROBABLY THE LITTLE BUGS
OR WHATEVER THEY ARE
HAVE NO APPETITE

263
00:16:34,076 --> 00:16:36,203
FOR GREEN BLOOD.

264
00:16:36,329 --> 00:16:39,749
BEING
A RED-BLOODED HUMAN

265
00:16:39,874 --> 00:16:43,169
OBVIOUSLY HAS
ITS DISADVANTAGES.

266
00:16:44,671 --> 00:16:46,923
THERE YOU HAVE
A MUSEUM PIECE, DOCTOR.

267
00:16:47,047 --> 00:16:50,134
LENS TYPE--
MANUALLY OPERATED,
LIGHT-ACTIVATED.

268
00:16:50,259 --> 00:16:53,137
SPARE ME THE ANALYSIS,
MR. SPOCK, PLEASE.

269
00:16:53,262 --> 00:16:55,389
IT IS ENOUGH
THAT IT WORKS.

270
00:17:01,395 --> 00:17:03,648
IT SPREADS
REAL FAST. I KNOW.

271
00:17:03,773 --> 00:17:06,484
WHEN YOU'RE OLD,
IT COVERS YOU
LIKE ANYTHING.

272
00:17:18,162 --> 00:17:20,790
"INTERMEDIATE
EXPERIMENTATION
REPORT PROJECT

273
00:17:20,915 --> 00:17:22,208
ON LIFE..."

274
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:25,336
"PROLONGATION."

275
00:17:27,171 --> 00:17:28,923
"PROGRESS REPORT--

276
00:17:29,048 --> 00:17:32,677
GENETICS SECTION,
LIFE PROLONGATION PROJECT."

277
00:17:32,802 --> 00:17:34,637
THAT'S WHAT IT WAS.

278
00:17:39,976 --> 00:17:42,478
LIFE PROLONGATION.

279
00:17:42,603 --> 00:17:45,147
DIDN'T HAVE
MUCH LUCK, DID THEY?

280
00:17:49,527 --> 00:17:50,152
CAPTAIN'S LOG.

281
00:17:50,277 --> 00:17:52,780
DR. McCOY'S BIOCOMPUTER

282
00:17:52,906 --> 00:17:54,908
AND A PORTABLE
ELECTRONIC MICROSCOPE

283
00:17:55,033 --> 00:17:56,367
HAVE BEEN BEAMED DOWN
FROM THE ENTERPRISE.

284
00:17:56,492 --> 00:17:58,619
THEY WILL BE
USED IN CONJUNCTION

285
00:17:58,745 --> 00:18:00,705
WITH COMPUTER BANKS
ON-BOARD SHIP.

286
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:02,916
TUBULAR WITH
EXTREME MULTIPLICABILITY.

287
00:18:03,041 --> 00:18:06,544
APPEAR TO HAVE AFFINITY
FOR NUCLEIC ACIDS...

288
00:18:09,797 --> 00:18:11,173
THIS WAS
300 YEARS AGO, CAPTAIN.

289
00:18:11,298 --> 00:18:14,052
ALL THE ADULTS ARE DEAD.

290
00:18:14,176 --> 00:18:16,930
ONLY THE CHILDREN
ARE LEFT ALIVE.

291
00:18:17,055 --> 00:18:19,849
BUT CHILDREN
BECOME ADULTS.

292
00:18:19,974 --> 00:18:23,185
AT LEAST...
THEY HAVE UP TO NOW.

293
00:18:32,486 --> 00:18:34,030
DOCTOR?

294
00:18:35,155 --> 00:18:37,909
THERE ARE CERTAIN
GLANDULAR CHANGES

295
00:18:38,034 --> 00:18:40,160
WHICH TAKE PLACE
UPON ENTERING PUBERTY,

296
00:18:40,286 --> 00:18:41,161
ARE THERE NOT?

297
00:18:41,287 --> 00:18:43,122
OF COURSE.

298
00:18:43,247 --> 00:18:45,374
IT CHANGES THE ENTIRE
BODY SYSTEM.

299
00:18:45,499 --> 00:18:46,292
YOU KNOW THAT.

300
00:18:46,417 --> 00:18:49,712
OF COURSE YOU KNOW THAT.
WHY?

301
00:18:49,837 --> 00:18:54,759
IS IT NOT POSSIBLE
THAT THESE CHILDREN HERE,

302
00:18:54,884 --> 00:18:57,511
AS THEY ENTER PUBERTY,
CONTRACT THE DISEASE?

303
00:18:57,637 --> 00:18:59,138
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN

304
00:18:59,263 --> 00:19:01,099
WHY THERE ARE
NO ADULTS.

305
00:19:01,223 --> 00:19:04,268
GLANDULAR...

306
00:19:04,393 --> 00:19:06,104
POSTPUBESCENT.

307
00:19:06,228 --> 00:19:07,897
IT COULD BE.

308
00:19:09,148 --> 00:19:11,067
IT'S ILLOGICAL.

309
00:19:11,191 --> 00:19:12,902
IT DOES NOT FOLLOW.

310
00:19:13,027 --> 00:19:15,362
ALL THE ADULTS
ON THIS PLANET DIED

311
00:19:15,488 --> 00:19:17,740
300 YEARS AGO,

312
00:19:17,865 --> 00:19:21,285
BUT THERE ARE CHILDREN
IN THE STREETS.

313
00:19:21,410 --> 00:19:24,705
WHO DIE WHEN THEY
ENTER ADOLESCENCE.

314
00:19:26,082 --> 00:19:28,835
BUT...HOW DO THEY
KEEP THE LINE GOING?

315
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:31,462
ONE THING, CAPTAIN.

316
00:19:31,587 --> 00:19:33,673
IF SHE WERE
A WILD ANIMAL

317
00:19:33,798 --> 00:19:35,508
EVER SINCE SHE'S
BEEN A LITTLE GIRL,

318
00:19:35,633 --> 00:19:37,010
HOW DO YOU EXPLAIN

319
00:19:37,135 --> 00:19:38,469
THAT SHE WANTS
TO STAY WITH US?

320
00:19:38,594 --> 00:19:40,387
LONELINESS.
I DON'T KNOW.
CURIOSITY.

321
00:19:40,513 --> 00:19:41,931
I THINK
CHILDREN HAVE
AN INSTINCTIVE NEED

322
00:19:42,056 --> 00:19:43,016
FOR ADULTS.

323
00:19:43,141 --> 00:19:46,268
THEY WANT TO BE TOLD
RIGHT AND WRONG.

324
00:19:46,393 --> 00:19:49,480
THERE MAY BE
OTHER EMOTIONS AT WORK

325
00:19:49,605 --> 00:19:50,356
IN THIS CASE, CAPTAIN.

326
00:19:50,481 --> 00:19:54,568
[McCOY]
SHE LIKES YOU, JIM.

327
00:19:54,694 --> 00:19:57,864
SHE'S BECOMING
A WOMAN.

328
00:20:09,959 --> 00:20:11,377
MR. SPOCK.

329
00:20:11,502 --> 00:20:13,754
[COMMUNICATOR BEEPS]

330
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:14,463
SPOCK HERE.

331
00:20:14,588 --> 00:20:17,758
HERE ARE THOSE FIGURES
YOU ASKED FOR.

332
00:20:17,884 --> 00:20:20,178
12 TO THE 10th POWER.

333
00:20:22,138 --> 00:20:25,307
METABOLIC RATE--72%.

334
00:20:27,351 --> 00:20:29,145
PRODUCTION
OF NUCLEIC ACIDS

335
00:20:29,269 --> 00:20:31,898
REDUCED
TO 33% OF NORMAL.

336
00:20:34,942 --> 00:20:40,073
CONVENTIONAL
CHRONOLOGICAL
PROGRESSION--100 x 3.6.

337
00:20:40,198 --> 00:20:41,615
ACKNOWLEDGED, LIEUTENANT.

338
00:20:47,454 --> 00:20:49,582
I HAVE
THE CALCULATIONS NOW.

339
00:20:51,084 --> 00:20:52,334
TRY AGAIN.

340
00:20:52,459 --> 00:20:55,629
SEE IF YOU CAN
FIND ANYTHING OUTSIDE.

341
00:20:55,755 --> 00:20:59,550
HEY...CLEAN UP THAT DESK
FOR ME, WILL YOU?

342
00:20:59,675 --> 00:21:01,635
ALL RIGHT, JIM.

343
00:21:05,098 --> 00:21:07,767
ACCORDING TO THEIR
LIFE PROLONGATION PLAN,

344
00:21:07,892 --> 00:21:09,351
WHAT THEY THOUGHT
THEY WERE ACCOMPLISHING,

345
00:21:09,476 --> 00:21:11,562
A PERSON WOULD
AGE ONLY ONE MONTH

346
00:21:11,687 --> 00:21:14,481
FOR EVERY 100 YEARS
OF REAL TIME.

347
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:18,986
100 YEARS
AND ONLY ONE MONTH?

348
00:21:19,112 --> 00:21:22,240
EXACTLY, YEOMAN.

349
00:21:22,364 --> 00:21:24,951
EVIDENTLY THROUGH
SOME MISCALCULATION,

350
00:21:25,076 --> 00:21:27,745
THIS VIRUS ANNIHILATED
THE ENTIRE ADULT POPULATION

351
00:21:27,870 --> 00:21:29,705
IN A VERY SHORT PERIOD,

352
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:31,415
LEAVING
ONLY THE CHILDREN.

353
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:33,417
BUT THAT MEANS
THESE CHILDREN...

354
00:21:33,542 --> 00:21:36,963
COULD VERY WELL
BE IMMENSELY OLD.

355
00:21:37,088 --> 00:21:38,464
THAT WOULD CERTAINLY
ANSWER THE QUESTION

356
00:21:38,589 --> 00:21:40,133
OF WHAT HAPPENED
TO THEIR PARENTS.

357
00:21:40,258 --> 00:21:41,175
ANSWERS IT VERY WELL.

358
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:44,303
CHILDREN
WHO NEVER AGE...

359
00:21:44,428 --> 00:21:46,973
ETERNAL CHILDHOOD,
FILLED WITH PLAY...

360
00:21:47,098 --> 00:21:48,682
NO RESPONSIBILITIES.

361
00:21:48,808 --> 00:21:50,601
IT'S ALMOST
LIKE A DREAM.

362
00:21:50,726 --> 00:21:53,104
I WOULDN'T
EXAMINE THAT DREAM
TOO CLOSELY, YEOMAN.

363
00:21:53,229 --> 00:21:55,856
IT MIGHT NOT
TURN OUT TO BE
VERY PRETTY.

364
00:21:55,982 --> 00:21:58,776
A FEW DAYS AGO
OR A WEEK AGO

365
00:21:58,901 --> 00:22:01,570
THAT CREATURE
THAT ATTACKED US

366
00:22:01,695 --> 00:22:04,364
COULD HAVE BEEN
JUST LIKE MIRI.

367
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:07,910
A CHILD ENTERING PUBERTY
ON THIS PLANET

368
00:22:08,035 --> 00:22:09,787
MEANS A DEATH SENTENCE.

369
00:22:11,747 --> 00:22:13,958
DO YOU SUPPOSE
SHE KNOWS?

370
00:22:15,209 --> 00:22:17,003
I DON'T THINK SO.

371
00:22:17,128 --> 00:22:19,338
IF THEY'RE AS OLD
AS SPOCK CLAIMS,

372
00:22:19,463 --> 00:22:22,382
THEY MUST HAVE SOME IDEA
OF WHAT'S HAPPENING.

373
00:22:22,508 --> 00:22:24,260
THERE'S NO ADULT
INTERPRETATION.

374
00:22:24,384 --> 00:22:26,762
I THINK
WE'RE DEALING
WITH CHILDREN,

375
00:22:26,887 --> 00:22:28,388
IMMENSELY OLD
PERHAPS,

376
00:22:28,514 --> 00:22:29,890
BUT NONETHELESS
CHILDREN.

377
00:22:30,016 --> 00:22:32,768
WE'VE GOT
TO DO SOMETHING
ABOUT THE OTHERS.

378
00:22:32,893 --> 00:22:34,645
DIFFICULT.
WE CAN'T EVEN GET
A GLIMPSE OF THEM.

379
00:22:34,770 --> 00:22:37,690
YOU COULDN'T
GET CLOSE
TO THE OTHER KIDS?

380
00:22:37,815 --> 00:22:38,941
IMPOSSIBLE.

381
00:22:39,066 --> 00:22:40,400
THEY KNOW THE AREA
TOO WELL,

382
00:22:40,526 --> 00:22:42,111
LIKE MICE.

383
00:22:42,236 --> 00:22:44,571
I'M GOING TO TRY.

384
00:22:48,284 --> 00:22:49,660
MIRI?

385
00:22:52,079 --> 00:22:53,622
COME HERE.

386
00:22:59,962 --> 00:23:01,588
YOU WANT TO GO
SOMEPLACE WITH ME?

387
00:23:01,714 --> 00:23:02,548
SURE.

388
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:18,314
THAT LITTLE GIRL...

389
00:23:18,438 --> 00:23:22,526
IS AT LEAST
300 YEARS OLDER
THAN YOU ARE, YEOMAN.

390
00:23:22,651 --> 00:23:25,363
THINK ABOUT IT.

391
00:23:50,512 --> 00:23:51,972
MIRI IS WITH THEM!

392
00:23:52,098 --> 00:23:52,806
WHY?

393
00:23:52,932 --> 00:23:54,308
WHY?

394
00:23:54,432 --> 00:23:55,976
WHAT'S SHE GOING
TO DO, JAHN?

395
00:23:56,102 --> 00:23:59,313
I DON'T--I DON'T KNOW.

396
00:23:59,437 --> 00:24:00,898
I KNOW WHAT
WE'VE GOT TO DO.

397
00:24:01,023 --> 00:24:03,150
THERE ARE MORE OF THEM
THAN WE SEE.

398
00:24:03,276 --> 00:24:06,153
SOMEWHERE...

399
00:24:06,279 --> 00:24:07,947
UP IN THE SKY...

400
00:24:08,072 --> 00:24:10,616
MAYBE, SOMEWHERE.

401
00:24:10,741 --> 00:24:13,535
THEY TALK TO EACH OTHER
ALL THE TIME.

402
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:16,163
YOU KNOW GRUPS.
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY DO--

403
00:24:16,289 --> 00:24:18,374
THE HURTING, THE KILLING.

404
00:24:18,498 --> 00:24:20,334
I REMEMBER, JAHN,
THE WAY IT WAS.

405
00:24:20,458 --> 00:24:21,919
THAT'S RIGHT,

406
00:24:22,044 --> 00:24:25,005
THE WAY IT WAS
IN THE BEFORE TIME.

407
00:24:28,675 --> 00:24:29,760
THEY TALK TO
THE OTHER GRUPS

408
00:24:29,885 --> 00:24:31,637
WITH THESE LITTLE BOXES.

409
00:24:34,848 --> 00:24:38,644
NOW, IF THEY DIDN'T HAVE
THOSE LITTLE BOXES,

410
00:24:38,769 --> 00:24:42,773
THEY'D BE...ALL ALONE.

411
00:24:42,898 --> 00:24:44,608
HUH?

412
00:24:44,733 --> 00:24:45,818
BUT THEY
DON'T SEE US.

413
00:24:45,943 --> 00:24:47,778
WE HIDE.

414
00:24:47,903 --> 00:24:50,739
OLLY OLLY OXEN FREE!
OLLY OLLY OXEN FREE!

415
00:24:50,864 --> 00:24:53,993
OLLY OLLY OXEN FREE!
OLLY OLLY OXEN FREE!

416
00:24:54,118 --> 00:24:55,328
NO!

417
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:58,456
IT'S NOT A GAME.

418
00:24:59,790 --> 00:25:01,583
IT'S REAL.

419
00:25:03,085 --> 00:25:04,670
THEY'RE DANGEROUS.
THEY'RE GRUPS.

420
00:25:04,795 --> 00:25:05,796
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND?

421
00:25:05,921 --> 00:25:07,589
JAHN!

422
00:25:21,479 --> 00:25:22,688
All right!

423
00:25:22,813 --> 00:25:24,606
Let's hide!

424
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:49,631
[THUMP]

425
00:25:52,218 --> 00:25:54,970
[CHILDREN SCREAM]

426
00:25:56,472 --> 00:25:57,890
AAH!

427
00:26:09,735 --> 00:26:11,195
AAH!

428
00:26:24,833 --> 00:26:26,626
DEAD.

429
00:26:26,752 --> 00:26:28,170
I DON'T UNDERSTAND IT.

430
00:26:28,295 --> 00:26:30,588
MY PHASER WASN'T
SET TO KILL.

431
00:26:34,176 --> 00:26:37,388
HER NAME WAS LOUISE.

432
00:26:37,513 --> 00:26:39,723
SHE WAS JUST
A LITTLE BIT OLDER
THAN I AM

433
00:26:39,848 --> 00:26:42,142
WHEN IT HAPPENED.

434
00:26:43,685 --> 00:26:45,020
OH, JIM.

435
00:26:53,904 --> 00:26:56,323
DATA HAS BEEN FED
INTO THE COMPUTERS,
MR. SPOCK.

436
00:26:56,449 --> 00:26:57,533
STAND BY.

437
00:26:57,657 --> 00:26:59,201
ACKNOWLEDGED.

438
00:26:59,326 --> 00:27:00,536
ARE THESE ENOUGH, JIM?

439
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:03,456
WE COULD USE MORE,
IF YOU DON'T MIND.

440
00:27:03,581 --> 00:27:05,916
NO, I DON'T MIND.

441
00:27:15,551 --> 00:27:20,139
THERE COULDN'T BE
ANY DOUBT ABOUT
WHAT YOU FOUND HERE?

442
00:27:20,264 --> 00:27:21,974
THIS FELLOW
MADE THESE NOTES

443
00:27:22,099 --> 00:27:24,768
IN THE LAST WEEKS
AFTER THE DISASTER BEGAN.

444
00:27:24,893 --> 00:27:28,814
I DISREGARD
THESE LAST ENTRIES.

445
00:27:28,939 --> 00:27:32,610
HE SAID HIMSELF
HE WAS TOO SICK,
TOO FAR GONE

446
00:27:32,734 --> 00:27:36,029
TO BE SURE HE WASN'T
ALREADY MAD, AND I AGREE,

447
00:27:36,155 --> 00:27:39,116
BUT BASED ON THE ENTRIES
HE MADE BEFORE THAT,

448
00:27:39,241 --> 00:27:41,952
I KNOW
HOW MUCH TIME WE HAVE.

449
00:27:42,077 --> 00:27:44,455
THE SHIP'S COMPUTERS
WILL VERIFY MY FIGURES.

450
00:27:44,580 --> 00:27:47,874
ONLY A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE WE ALL GO MAD,

451
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,502
DESTROY EACH OTHER,

452
00:27:49,627 --> 00:27:53,046
TILL THE LAST OF US
FINALLY DESTROYS
HIMSELF.

453
00:28:07,561 --> 00:28:09,104
WHAT ABOUT MIRI?

454
00:28:09,229 --> 00:28:10,981
OUR GUESS WAS CORRECT.

455
00:28:11,106 --> 00:28:12,732
THEY CONTRACT THE DISEASE

456
00:28:12,858 --> 00:28:15,361
AS THEY ENTER PUBERTY
AND THEIR METABOLISM
CHANGES.

457
00:28:15,486 --> 00:28:17,904
THE NOTES INDICATE
IT DOESN'T BECOME ACUTE

458
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,615
FOR A MONTH OR SO.

459
00:28:19,739 --> 00:28:24,119
I ESTIMATE SHE HAS PERHAPS
FIVE OR SIX WEEKS LEFT.

460
00:28:24,244 --> 00:28:25,078
WHAT ABOUT US?

461
00:28:25,204 --> 00:28:26,622
THE OLDER THE VICTIM,

462
00:28:26,746 --> 00:28:30,292
THE MORE RAPID THE PROGRESS
OF THE DISEASE.

463
00:28:33,170 --> 00:28:34,171
AND YOU?

464
00:28:34,296 --> 00:28:37,132
THE DISEASE DOESN'T SEEM
TO BE INTERESTED IN YOU.

465
00:28:37,257 --> 00:28:38,592
I AM A CARRIER.

466
00:28:38,717 --> 00:28:40,719
WHATEVER HAPPENS,
I CAN'T GO BACK
TO THE SHIP,

467
00:28:40,844 --> 00:28:45,807
AND I DO WANT TO GO
BACK TO THE SHIP, CAPTAIN.

468
00:28:48,101 --> 00:28:49,895
OF COURSE, MR. SPOCK.

469
00:28:52,606 --> 00:28:54,983
WE STILL DON'T KNOW
WHAT WE'RE FIGHTING.

470
00:28:55,108 --> 00:28:59,029
NO...BUT WE KNOW
WHAT IT IS AND
HOW FAST IT DOES IT.

471
00:28:59,154 --> 00:29:00,739
IT'S PROGRESSING.

472
00:29:00,864 --> 00:29:02,658
WE'LL BEGIN TO FEEL IT
INSIDE SOON--

473
00:29:02,782 --> 00:29:03,367
INTENSE FEVER,

474
00:29:03,492 --> 00:29:05,869
GREAT PAIN
IN THE EXTREMITIES,

475
00:29:05,994 --> 00:29:07,705
FUZZINESS OF VISION.

476
00:29:07,829 --> 00:29:10,040
OF COURSE, THOSE ARE
THE EARLY SYMPTOMS.

477
00:29:10,165 --> 00:29:12,834
THERE'LL BE MORE.

478
00:29:14,378 --> 00:29:16,463
ARE YOU CERTAIN
ABOUT THE TIME
WE HAVE LEFT?

479
00:29:16,589 --> 00:29:19,258
I PRESUME MY CALCULATIONS
ARE CORRECT.

480
00:29:19,383 --> 00:29:20,718
IS THERE
ANY POSSIBILITY--

481
00:29:20,842 --> 00:29:21,968
LANDING PARTY,
THIS IS THE<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

482
00:29:22,094 --> 00:29:24,137
SPOCK HERE.

483
00:29:24,263 --> 00:29:27,558
COMPUTER INDICATES
170 HOURS, MR. SPOCK.

484
00:29:27,683 --> 00:29:29,393
VERIFIED, CAPTAIN.

